### 測試資料庫初始化
# 注意：這些 API 端點需要先實作認證系統才能使用
# 這裡只是展示預期的 API 結構

### 註冊新使用者
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 登入
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 取得使用者資料
GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 新增地點
POST http://localhost:3001/api/locations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "測試咖啡廳",
  "description": "一家很棒的咖啡廳",
  "address": "台北市信義區信義路五段7號",
  "latitude": 25.0330,
  "longitude": 121.5654,
  "category": "咖啡廳",
  "rating": 5,
  "notes": "環境很棒，咖啡很好喝"
}

### 取得使用者的所有地點
GET http://localhost:3001/api/locations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 取得特定地點
GET http://localhost:3001/api/locations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 更新地點
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/locations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4,
  "notes": "更新後的備註"
}

### 刪除地點
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/locations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 篩選地點（按分類）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/locations?category=咖啡廳
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 搜尋地點
GET http://localhost:3001/api/locations?search=咖啡
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 取得地點統計
GET http://localhost:3001/api/locations/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
